item.content:encoded:
I love to mountain bike. But, as much as I love mountain biking, I don't ride when the trails are wet - it damages the trail. Walnut Creek is a system of popular mountain biking trails in Austin. It's where I ride most often and it's so popular that "is Austin dry?" became somewhat of a meme on a local biking message board. Clearly I wasn't the only one who wanted to know "is Walnut dry?
